---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import LegalLayout from '../../components/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE, NAP } from '../../lib/constants';

const title = `Cancellation policy · ${SITE.shortName}`;
const description = '100% refund up to 14 days before check-in, 50% up to 7 days. Detailed terms.';
const pathname = '/en/cancellation';
---
<Base locale="en" title={title} description={description} pathname={pathname}>
  <LegalLayout locale="en" eyebrow="Legal" title="Cancellation policy" updated="2026-05-09">
    <p>
      This is the base policy for direct bookings through <a href={SITE.url}>{SITE.url}</a>. If you
      booked via Airbnb or Booking, the policy of that channel applies.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Early-cancellation refunds</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>14 or more days before check-in:</strong> 100% refund.</li>
      <li><strong>Between 7 and 14 days before:</strong> 50% refund.</li>
      <li><strong>Less than 7 days before or no-show:</strong> non-refundable.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Date changes</h2>
    <p>
      Subject to availability and to the rate difference for the new dates. For changes, message us
      on WhatsApp at <a href={`https://wa.me/${NAP.whatsapp}`}>{NAP.phoneDisplay}</a> with at least
      7 days notice.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Force majeure</h2>
    <p>
      For verified medical emergencies and other force-majeure events, contact us as soon as
      possible. We don’t guarantee a refund but we’ll work toward the best solution.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Cancellation by us</h2>
    <p>
      In the unlikely event we must cancel your booking for operational reasons, we’ll notify you
      as early as possible and refund 100% of the paid amount, or offer a unit of equal or better
      category.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Refund processing</h2>
    <p>
      Refunds are processed via the original payment method through Housy Host / Hostaway. Typical
      crediting time is 5–10 business days.
    </p>
  </LegalLayout>
</Base>
